<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">إِذَا قَالَ:</span> إِنْ حِضْتِ فَأَنْتِ طَالِقٌ: طَلَقَتْ بِأَوَّلِ حَيْضٍ مُتَيَقَّنٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي:</span> إِذَا حِضْتِ حَيْضَةً: تَطْلُقُ بِأَوَّلِ الطُّهْرِ مِنْ حَيْضَةٍ كَامِلَةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي:</span> إِذَا حِضْتِ نِصْفَ حَيْضَةٍ: تَطْلُقُ فِي نِصْفِ عَادَتِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>